server:
1、wireguard-install
curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/angristan/wireguard-install/master/wireguard-install.sh
chmod +x wireguard-install.sh
sudo ./wireguard-install.sh

2、交互式安装：
Welcome to the WireGuard installer!
I need to ask you a few questions before starting the setup.
You can leave the default options and just press enter if you are ok with them.

IPv4 or IPv6 public address: [your-server-public-ip] ← 自动检测，回车
Public interface: eth0 ← 通常是 eth0 或 ens3，回车
WireGuard interface name: wg0 ← 默认，回车
Server's WireGuard IPv4: 10.8.0.1 ← 默认虚拟网关，回车
Server's WireGuard IPv6: 建议跳过（除非你需要 IPv6）
Server's WireGuard port [51820]: ← 默认端口，回车
First DNS resolver: 8.8.8.8 ← 推荐 Google DNS
Second DNS resolver (optional): 1.1.1.1 ← Cloudflare DNS
Client name: mylaptop ← 给你的设备起个名字（如 mypc, iphone, nas）


3、生成客户端
mylaptop.conf

4、添加更多客户端
sudo ./wireguard-install.sh
1) Add a new client
输入新设备名（如 myphone）


========================================================================

client:
1、Windows 客户端
    下载安装：https://www.wireguard.com/install/
    打开 WireGuard → 点击 Import tunnel(s) from file
    选择 mylaptop.conf
    点击 Activate → 连接成功！
    
2、Android / iOS
    应用商店搜索 “WireGuard” 并安装
    点击 ➕ → Create from file or archive
    用微信/QQ/邮件/AirDrop 传 myphone.conf 到手机
    导入 → 启用

3、linux
sudo apt update && sudo apt install wireguard resolvconf -y  # Ubuntu/Debian
# 或
sudo yum install epel-release wireguard-tools -y            # CentOS 8+
sudo dnf install wireguard-tools -y                         # CentOS 9+/Fedora

sudo cp mylaptop.conf /etc/wireguard/wg0.conf
sudo systemctl enable wg-quick@wg0
sudo systemctl start wg-quick@wg0

sudo wg show
